{
  "stem": "25639.7",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The interesting-- an interesting thing happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I finally returned to Hannover for the first time, that was in 1947.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm sorry, in 1987-- correction. '87.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was very anxious to visit the Continental Gummi-Werke, but I didn't know how.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This trip was a filming trip for-- for the documentary film that we were working on when I was 14, And I wanted to take this opportunity to see the factory where I labored as a-- as a young girl.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I asked the crew if they had any ideas, and none came forward.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said well, I had in mind just go there and knock on the door and tell them that a long time ago, I worked here and I wanted to see how the place changed.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, they laughed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I was perfectly serious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Not having had a better idea, this was what I was going to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I didn't have to do that, because, at this time, I also had the occasion to-- to speak from a platform to unveil a memorial stone to the Holocaust victims lost at the Continental Gummi-Werke, actually.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was honored to do this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And while we were there, we scouted the place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I-- I had certain landmarks in mind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were two canals.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I could just visualize the slave laborers around the-- the banks of the canals.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we couldn't find them for a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But we-- of course, we did, after we looked at an aerial map from Washington, DC.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This aerial map showed that there were no trees along the banks of the canal yet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But when we returned-- when I returned with the film crew-- there all these trees which prevented-- prevented us from seeing the canal.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
